      "butter_on_bread_frequency_opt_8": "2 or More Times Per Day",
      "pxt50801_orange_juice_frequency": "Think about your eating habits over the past 12 months. About how often did you drink Orange juice or grapefruit juice? Remember breakfast, lunch, dinner, snacks, and eating out. Choose only one answer.",
      "pxt50801_orange_juice_frequency_opt_1": "Never",
      "pxt50801_orange_juice_frequency_opt_2": "Less than Once Per Month",
