      "pxt50801_orange_juice_frequency_opt_7": "1 Time Per Day",
      "pxt50801_orange_juice_frequency_opt_8": "2 or More Times Per Day",
      "pxt50801_fruit_frequency": "Think about your eating habits over the past 12 months. About how often did you eat Fruit (not juices)? Remember breakfast, lunch, dinner, snacks, and eating out. Choose only one answer.",
